bindheader: Bind the {{drops}} currently selected {{itemnames}} to your account. This will lock them to your account, set the {{itemnames}} to use the accounts RAM, and release the EOS value of the RAM in the contract.
claimbalance: Claim any remaining balance in contract?
destroyheader: This action will destroy the {{drops}} selected {{itemnames}} and reclaim the resources they use.
estimationwaiting: Select one or more {{itemnames}} to begin estimation.
rambalanceuse: Your RAM contract balance to use
ramtorelease: Your RAM that will be released
signinfirst: 您必须登录才能查看您的 {{itemnames}}。
subheader: 您的帐户当前拥有的 {{itemnames}} 数量（按纪元）。
transferboundwarningtext: 您尝试转移的一项或多项{{itemnames}} 已绑定到您的帐户。 您必须先解除绑定，然后才能转移它们。
transferdescription: 将当前选定的 {{drops}} {{itemnames}} 的所有权转移到下面输入的帐户名。
unbindheader: 取消绑定当前选定的 {{drops}} {{itemnames}}。 这将解锁 {{itemnames}} 以使其可交易，将其设置为使用合约 RAM，并将 RAM 的 EOS 值锁定在合约中。
unbindunboundwarningtext: One or more of the {{itemnames}} you are trying to unbind is not bound to your account.
